headline.print_headline: Hundreds Paddle Out to Recall Drowned Lifeguard
headline.main: Hundreds Paddle Out to Recall Drowned Lifeguard

lead_paragraph: Hundreds of surfers paddled out on boards to remember a Southern California lifeguard who drowned a week ago while saving a swimmer caught in treacherous surf.
